'''Binka''' were a type of tree that grew regularly spaced in forests on [[Agamar/Legends|Agamar]]. They were known to bear edible [[Binka fruit]]. A binka forest grew between [[Calna Muun]] and [[Tondatha]].

[[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]] used to practice maneuvers around them in his [[T-16 skyhopper/Legends|T-16 skyhopper]].

